HEALTH SERVICES. Provides relative to comprehensive weight management services.
(8/1/26)
1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 42:855, relative to comprehensive weight management services; to provide
3 for authority of the Office of Group Benefits; to provide for covered services; and
4 to provide for related matters.
5 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
6 Section 1. R.S. 42:855 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
7 §855. Office of Group Benefits; comprehensive weight management services
8 The Office of Group benefits may contract with qualified healthcare
9 providers, pharmacy partners, and program administrators to provide
10 comprehensive weight management services for plan participants, including
11 FDA-approved medications and clinically appropriate compounded therapies,
12 together with medical evaluation, prescribing oversight, follow-up care, and
13 related support services.
